{"id":24762,"date":"2017-05-03T10:53:36","date_gmt":"2017-05-03T06:53:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=24762"},"modified":"2025-07-26T11:08:23","modified_gmt":"2025-07-26T07:08:23","slug":"prophet-eat-sit-as-servant","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/03\/prophet-eat-sit-as-servant\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Humility: I eat as a servant eats, as a servant sits"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>O Aisha, if I had wished, a mountain of gold would have been sent with me. An angel came to me whose belt was like the Ka\u2019bah. He said: Verily, your Lord sends you greetings of peace and He says, if you wish, you may be a prophet-servant or a prophet-king. I looked to Gabriel and he indicated that I should humble myself, so I said I will be a prophet-servant<\/strong>.\u201d After that, the Prophet never ate while reclining and he would say, \u201c<strong>I eat as the servant eats, and I sit as the servant sits.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad Abi\u0304 Ya\u2019la\u0301 4920<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em>Hasan<\/em> (fair) according to Al-Haythami<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u00a0\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0644\u064e\u0648\u0652 \u0634\u0650\u0626\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0644\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a \u062c\u0650\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064f \u0627\